 the wrong forum. We have a number of different forums for a reason. Please post in the correct place.<br><br>b) Cross Posting. Never post the same thing in more than 1 forum.<br><br>c) Violation of the signature rules.<br><br>d) Posting all in capitals. Especially thread titles. Threads all in caps WILL be deleted.<br><br>3) Signatures must be kept below 50kb in size. Flash/shockwave animations are allowed, as long as they are below this size. Remember, not everyone is on broadband.<br><br>4) Scripts that produce 'mouse-over' graphical effects on images in signatures are not allowed, as they have been proven to cause problems for some users.<br><br>5) A signature should be no deeper than 10 lines of text, including images, and should not be so wide as to cause the window to extend on a 800x600 display.<br><br>6) Under no circumstance should sound be included in any thread, and this includes signatures.<br><br>Continued violations of rules in the above section can and will result in a warning, and possibly a ban.<br><br>The main rule is this:<br><br>Remember this is a game that we play to have fun. Posting here should be just as enjoyable for all users, as playing EQ<br><br>The above posting ruled have been copied from, and used with permission by Zadkiel, from www.monkly-business.com  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathholyswordsandquests.showPrevMessage?topicID=3289.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathholyswordsandquests.showNextMessage?topicID=3289.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathholyswordsandquests.emailToFriend?topicID=3289.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend">